name: Fish Oil
description: A bladder filled with fish oil. This would make excellent fertilizer.

name: Bundle of Seeds
description: A package of seeds used by the Sylvari to grow their plantlike architecture.

name: Spring Water
description: Crystal clear water. Perfect for growing Sylvari architecture.

name: Energy Crystal
description: This crystal is humming with a faint energy. There was once an inscription, but the only legible part reads "Oo...""

name: Merchant Remains
description:
Remains of a slain Merchant.
Event Item.

name: Dolyak Sinew
description: This tough sinew can be turned into thread by Seamstress Aina.

name: Hylek Armor
description: This armor was most likely stolen from the local hylek. It should be returned to Yoal east of Titan's Staircase.

name: Caledon Lavender
description: This flower is used by sylvari for medicine. Harvester Mavad near Gleaner's Cove Waypoint could likely use it.

name: Chunk of Scourgejaw Iron
description: This iron is valuable to Scourgejaw guards.

name: Piece of Kelp
description: The hylek use this plant for reducing toxicity in their bodies. A hylek village should be nearby where someone can make use of this.

name: Supplies
description: Someone in the nearby Pact base to the north would like this.

name: Dwarven Key
description: Event Item. Looks like it would open a very old lock.

name: Containment Crystal
description: Event Item. A mysteriously glowing shard of crystal.
